      </div>

      <!-- assessment criteria -->
      <div class="LessonContent__section">

        <div class="LessonContent__heading">Assessment Criteria</div>

        <div class="LesssonContent__text">

          <p>
            Your students should know the following things:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>What are the benefits of modeling small, separate pieces for printing?</li>
            <li>What tools do you use to build objects in Tinkercad?</li>
            <li>What are the strengths and weaknesses of Tinkercad?</li>
            <li>How do you navigate in Tinkercad?</li>
            <li>When building the mountain tiles, why was it important to use the Hole tool to cut off	the base of the tile?</li>
            <li>What are the benefits of plating multiple prints at a time?</li>
          </ul>

        </div>

